<L>"With thou&s;and others, who&s;e mi&s;hapen frame</L>
<L>"Still balks de&s;cription, and &s;till wants a name<NOTE N="*" PLACE="foot">We ob&s;erve the <HI>Ari&s;tocrat</HI> throughout this pa&s;&s;age. ARISTUS gradually di&s;covers him&s;elf to the ENVOY. <HI>Unfunded Paper</HI> is ranked among the plagues of a country. <HI>Exci&s;e</HI> and <HI>Impo&s;t,</HI> too, are put in the li&s;t; but the real meaning mu&s;t be &s;hewn. ARISTUS is &s;peaking of the times preceding the pre&s;ent Con&s;titution, when an unequal Impo&s;t and Exci&s;e were levied in &s;everal of the States. This it is that excites his hate; not that univer&s;al burthen, under which, good democrats now groan.</NOTE>.</L>
</LG>
<LG>
<PB N="12" REF="028172_0010_0FD734950164DB78">
<L>"While thus, from day to day, from hour to hour,</L>
