<L>"And &s;elfi&s;h <GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="UOM" EXTENT="1 word">&mdash;in conte&s;ts fierce engag'd;</L>
<L>"And each, at home, to di&s;cord dire a prey,</L>
<L>"Saw threat'ning clouds deform the beauteous day;</L>
<L>"As the la&s;t project to protract their fate,</L>
<L>"The <HI>&s;elf-call'd</HI><NOTE N="*" PLACE="foot">This &s;eems to be a very awkward and ob&s;cure &s;neer upon the Fe|deral Convention of 1787; the epithet "&s;elf-call'd" being equivocal; tho' de&s;igned, as I &s;uppo&s;e, to convey the &s;ame meaning with the French expre&s;&s;ion <HI>&s;oi-di&s;ant.</HI> ARISTUS, the enemy of Republicani&s;m, <GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="UOM" EXTENT="1 span"> involve, in one general cen&s;ure, all who &s;avour it, in any &s;hape.</NOTE> &s;ages of the nation met.</L>
<L>"(The pledge his honour)&mdash;what&s;oe'er he hears&mdash;</L>
