<LG>
<L>Here tears of angui&s;h, &s;uch as, er&s;t, in Heaven,</L>
<L>When from their &s;eats his haughty pow'rs were driv'n,</L>
<L>From SATAN fell&mdash;ARISTUS &s;hed: his rage,</L>
<L>The bitter drops, &s;low falling, half a&s;&s;uage;</L>
